      "blocks": {
        "text_9VGbY4": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "richtext": "<p>We’re Gntl. We believe in a world of radically minimalist essentials, where every item on our shelf holds meaning, beauty, and function. We make facial-quality skincare for the entire body and embrace the luxury of less.</p><p>Our simplified, thoughtfully crafted, multi-functional formulas serve all bodies, skin types, and stages of life. By reducing the number of products in our routines, we create space for something greater: meaningful connections with ourselves and the world around us that are more than skin-deep.<br/><br/>Gntl is a call to slow down, honor our bodies with intimate care, and make conscious choices that are gentler on the planet. The more we simplify, the more we savor the small moments: the soft rhythm of rain against a window, the warm glow of a sunset on the horizon, the scent of sandalwood drifting through the air, and the pleasure of suds sliding over damp skin.<br/><br/>Gntl is a celebration of radical simplicity—a return to the essentials and a gentle reminder that all you need is less.</p>",
            "text_size": 5
          }
        }
