            "text": "<p>The skincare industry equates efficacy with an endless stream of products, convincing us that more steps, more ingredients, and more purchases are the only ways to achieve results. Behind the scenes, we know that’s not true: it’s overconsumption disguised as self-care.</p><p>Our solution? Thoughtfully crafted, multi-functional formulas designed to nourish all skin, head to toe. With fewer, better ingredients, Gntl offers a more effective approach to self-care — one that delivers real results while being kinder to both our bodies and the planet.</p>",
