            "kicker": "",
            "title": "A note from our founder",
            "text": "<p>Sydney Dake is a product developer and brand builder with a knack for creating innovative, viral beauty solutions. She’s developed some of your most beloved cosmetic and skincare products and helped build mission-driven beauty startups.<br/><br/></p><h6>In my years in the beauty industry, I saw firsthand how the market pushes excess. I believe we've been conditioned to equate efficacy with an endless stream of products and steps—when in reality, results come from doing less, but doing it well. My approach to care is rooted in the belief that 80% of your results come from just 20% of your effort, and that self-care should be a practice in mindfulness, not excess.<br/><br/>xo, Sydney Dake </h6>",
